The paper discusses the deployment of distributed applications in multi-cloud environments using Aneka platform. This involves resource provisioning from different cloud providers, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses the architecture and extensions of Aneka platform, which can be categorized under Computer Engineering (cs.CE). The inclusion of public IPs and the use of PowerShell for installation can be categorized under Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the deployment and execution of applications, which can be categorized under Software Engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper focuses on the use of multi-cloud environments, which can be categorized under Distributed Systems (cs.Distributed Systems).
